---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /find-a-doctor.html
title: Find a doctor
description: "A community-built directory of doctors who diagnose and treat RCPD (no-burp syndrome). Search by name, city, state, or country."
scripts:
  - /assets/js/doctors.js
---

<section class="page-head section section--tight">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Directory</p>
    <h1>Find a doctor</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      A directory of clinicians who diagnose and treat RCPD, compiled by the community. Search
      by name, clinic, city, state, or country to find someone near you.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="callout callout--note">
      <p>
        <strong>How this directory is sourced.</strong> These clinicians are compiled from the
        community-maintained <a href="{{ site.reddit }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">r/noburp</a>
        specialists map &mdash; doctors that patients have reported as treating RCPD with Botox.
        Listing here is <strong>not</strong> an endorsement or a guarantee of treatment, and most
        entries link to a general clinic or hospital profile rather than an RCPD-specific page.
        Some clinicians publicly describe their RCPD work; for everyone else, please
        <strong>confirm the clinician currently treats RCPD when you contact them</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="finder__controls">
      <label class="visually-hidden" for="doctor-search">Search the directory</label>
      <input
        class="finder__search"
        type="search"
        id="doctor-search"
        name="doctor-search"
        placeholder="Search by name, city, state, or country&hellip;"
        autocomplete="off"
        spellcheck="false">
      <p class="finder__count" id="doctor-count" data-total="{{ doctors.length }}">
        {{ doctors.length }} doctors listed
      </p>
    </div>

    <p id="finder-empty" class="callout callout--note" hidden>
      No doctors match your search. Try a broader term &mdash; a state, province, or country.
    </p>

    <div class="doctor-grid" id="doctor-grid">
      {%- for doc in doctors %}
      <article class="doctor" data-search="{{ doc.search }}">
        <h2 class="doctor__name">{{ doc.name }}</h2>
        {% if doc.specialty %}<p class="doctor__specialty">{{ doc.specialty }}</p>{% endif %}
        {% if doc.clinic %}<p class="doctor__clinic">{{ doc.clinic }}</p>{% endif %}
        {% if doc.location %}<p class="doctor__location">{{ doc.location }}</p>{% endif %}
        {% if doc.phone or doc.website %}
        <div class="doctor__contact">
          {% if doc.phone %}<a href="{{ doc.phone | telHref }}">{{ doc.phone }}</a>{% endif %}
          {% if doc.website %}<a href="{{ doc.website }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit website</a>{% endif %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </article>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>

    <p class="figure-note" style="margin-top:2rem">
      This list is community-maintained and may be incomplete or out of date &mdash; always confirm
      a clinician treats RCPD before booking. Know a doctor who should be here? Share them with the
      <a href="{{ site.reddit }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">r/noburp</a> community.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
